## Biography

Simone Arianne Biles is widely considered the greatest gymnast in history. Born in Columbus, Ohio in 1997, she was raised in foster care as a young child before being adopted by her grandfather Ron Biles and his wife Nellie. She began gymnastics at age 6 and by 15 had won her first senior national championship. She has since accumulated 25 World Championship medals (a record) including 19 golds, and 7 Olympic medals (four golds in Rio 2016, three more in Tokyo/Paris). She is the only gymnast to ...

